Chapter: Eight is enough

def Byte: a thing that has a 8 separate LOCATIONS in SPACE
          eachof which can be either on or off, that a re kept in same order

          The byte as a whole is a thing that has a LOCATION in SPACE
          has the quality that any given time it is in ONE of 256 possible states
          It can be changed back and forth between these states

We now have a tool that can help us overcome the limitation stated in '4'
